   subject :  sinking ship

 Please believe me when I tell you I know
only as much as you lot do.
I cannot speak for Nick unless he tells
me the situation. As he has not said
anything new to me we must assume
nothing has changed as yet. I do know he
has had contact with other networks but
so far 'contact' is all. No deals etc.
As a remote Editor I can't tell you what
goes on at Cnet but I honestly don't
think there is anything to tell you
which you don't already know.
Please don't flood my MBX, when I am
told you will be told.  Regards Dral   ­ 
 This is sending waves of recollections
of the time in 1987. Then we had no
information what the hell was going on.
for weeks on end. Maybe nothing new, if
there isn't then why  not ?  Surely
that would be very bad news

